# mydiary

MyDiary is a simple API allowing consumers to write down their thoughts and emotions for later review.

## User Registration [/auth/signup]

### Create a New User [POST]

You may create a new user profile using this action. It takes a JSON
object containing a name, an email and a password.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "name": "Gordon Balaaka",
            "email": "myname@email.com",
            "password": "mypass"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                "user": {
                    "email": "myname@email.com",
                    "name": "Gordon Balaaka"
                }
            }


