## User Entries [/api/v1/entries]

### Create a New Entry [POST]

You may create a new diary entry using this action. It takes a JSON
object containing a the entry's data and title.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "entrydata": "This is my first diary entry",
            "entrytitle": "First Title"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJqdGkiOiIwMmE1ODk5Zi05YzJlLTQ0MDYtYTZhMS01OTQ2MWM5ZGQ0ZmYiLCJleHAiOjE1MzM2NTgzMzksImZyZXNoIjpmYWxzZSwiaWF0IjoxNTMzNjU0NzM5LCJ0eXBlIjoiYWNjZXNzIiwibmJmIjoxNTMzNjU0NzM5LCJpZGVudGl0eSI6MTZ9.gIE30xpZXhk17c0KAXznwu6h22ek1ko-IfLB7uHpolo

    + Body

            {
                "entry added": {
                    "datecreated": "7/8/2018",
                    "entrydata": "first diary entry",
                    "title": "First Title",
                    "user_id": 16
                },
                "message": "Entry added successfully"
            }


